<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <title>Withdrawal Initiated</title>
</head>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background: #f5f5f5; padding: 20px;">
  <div style="max-width: 500px; margin: 0 auto; background: white; border-radius: 12px; padding: 32px;">
    <h2 style="color: #F47C20; margin-bottom: 8px;">Withdrawal Initiated 🏦</h2>
    <p style="color: #333;">Hi {{firstName}},</p>
    <p style="color: #555;">Your withdrawal request has been received and is being processed.</p>

    <div style="background: #f9f9f9; border-radius: 8px; padding: 16px; margin: 20px 0;">
      <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 13px; color: #888;">Amount</p>
      <p style="margin: 4px 0 0; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; color: #F47C20;">₦{{amount}}</p>
    </div>

    <p style="color: #555; font-size: 13px;">Bank: <strong>{{bankName}}</strong></p>
    <p style="color: #555; font-size: 13px;">Account Number: <strong>{{accountNumber}}</strong></p>
    <p style="color: #555; font-size: 13px;">Reference: <strong>{{reference}}</strong></p>
    <p style="color: #555; font-size: 13px;">Date: <strong>{{date}}</strong></p>

    <p style="color: #555; font-size: 13px; margin-top: 20px;">
      Funds will be sent to your bank account within <strong>24 hours</strong>.
    </p>

    <p style="color: #888; font-size: 12px; margin-top: 32px;">
      If you did not initiate this withdrawal, please contact support immediately.
    </p>

    <p style="color: #888; font-size: 12px;">— The Sendrey Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html>